  "text": "This work first simulates the uniform rectangular cantilever beam micro-tweezers addressed in the references [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] to confirm the accuracy and feasibility of the proposed DQM approach. The current simulation results are then compared with those presented in the relevant literature.",
